I had this old Ruby script lying around which I was using to upload my sites to s3 whenever I wanted to deploy something new.
However, as you can imagine, copying this script around was not the best solution as in time, I added bits here and there, updated to use new aws-sdk etc, and keeping them all in sync was getting tedious &hellip;
Sooo, finally I nudged myself and put it in a gem.
